1
00:00:01,084 --> 00:00:04,212
[Axl] <i>You're giving us</i>
<i>high-caliber weapons for free?</i>

2
00:00:04,295 --> 00:00:05,296
<i>Is there a catch?</i>

3
00:00:05,380 --> 00:00:07,632
[Felix] <i>You'll rob a bank</i>
<i>using those weapons.</i>

4
00:00:07,716 --> 00:00:09,092
<i>Let's do it 50-50!</i>

5
00:00:09,175 --> 00:00:12,846
<i>Just don't give me a hard time.</i>

6
00:00:12,929 --> 00:00:15,056
Keep a close eye on the CCTVs.

7
00:00:15,140 --> 00:00:16,975
<i>Keep your eyes on the TFA.</i>

8
00:00:17,058 --> 00:00:19,436
[Axl] If you want the people in here
to come out alive,

9
00:00:19,519 --> 00:00:22,564
- give us our demands. A helicopter.
- Alright!

10
00:00:22,647 --> 00:00:23,606
[Lara, in Engilsh] <i>Marcus,</i>
<i>you have 30 minutes.</i>

11
00:00:24,190 --> 00:00:25,525
- [in English] Copy.
- [Azuelo] <i>I can't let you</i>

12
00:00:25,608 --> 00:00:26,651
<i>be the only ones happy.</i>

13
00:00:26,735 --> 00:00:30,030
<i>I want you to release ten hostages.</i>

14
00:00:30,113 --> 00:00:31,489
- [people weeping]
- [man] You! Go join them too!

15
00:00:31,573 --> 00:00:32,657
[Jamilah] <i>No!</i>

16
00:00:32,741 --> 00:00:35,243
Prioritize the patients! They matter more!

17
00:00:35,326 --> 00:00:36,661
Whatever!

18
00:00:37,704 --> 00:00:40,457
[Azuelo] <i>But the moment we see blood,</i>

19
00:00:40,540 --> 00:00:44,544
<i>my men will rush in</i>
<i>and make sure you never get out.</i>

20
00:00:44,627 --> 00:00:46,171
- What are you doing?!
- Doctor!

21
00:00:46,254 --> 00:00:47,130
- Put him in the wheelchair.
- [Teresa] Huh?

22
00:00:47,213 --> 00:00:49,048
We can't! His wounds are still fresh!

23
00:00:49,132 --> 00:00:50,258
I don't care!

24
00:00:51,760 --> 00:00:53,052
[Jovi] Be careful!

25
00:00:53,928 --> 00:00:55,889
- [sirens wailing]
- [Jovi] Quick!

26
00:00:55,972 --> 00:00:58,099
[Omar] <i>We'll break in. We'll save Jamilah.</i>

27
00:00:59,476 --> 00:01:01,352
[Lara, in English] <i>Agent Castillo,</i>
<i>hostile approaching your way.</i>

28
00:01:03,021 --> 00:01:03,938
[grunts]

29
00:01:05,023 --> 00:01:06,733
[thug] <i>Boss, the cameras are on a loop!</i>

30
00:01:07,442 --> 00:01:08,568
[grunts]

31
00:01:08,651 --> 00:01:10,028
You bastards!

32
00:01:10,111 --> 00:01:12,530
<i>I'm going to kill everyone!</i>

33
00:01:12,614 --> 00:01:14,532
[Lara, in English] <i>Espina,</i>
<i>standby for rendezvous with Agent Reyes.</i>

34
00:01:14,616 --> 00:01:15,992
<i>Be alert.</i>

35
00:01:18,620 --> 00:01:19,662
[grunts]

36
00:01:19,746 --> 00:01:21,372
- [rapid gunfire]
- [people screaming]

37
00:01:37,096 --> 00:01:43,520
[mysterious theme music playing]

38
00:01:52,153 --> 00:01:54,405
[tense music playing]

39
00:01:59,327 --> 00:02:00,453
Miss, are you alright?

40
00:02:01,704 --> 00:02:03,206
[policeman] Come on! Move! Move!

41
00:02:03,289 --> 00:02:04,666
Let's go! Let's go!

42
00:02:13,925 --> 00:02:15,051
[grunts]

43
00:02:15,135 --> 00:02:16,845
- [Jovi] Move!
- [Teresa] Let go of me!

44
00:02:16,928 --> 00:02:18,429
- [Axl] Don't be stubborn!
- [Teresa] Let go!

45
00:02:18,513 --> 00:02:19,973
- [Axl] Just do as I say!
- [Jovi] Come here!

46
00:02:20,056 --> 00:02:21,516
- [Jamilah] Doc!
- Let me go!

47
00:02:21,599 --> 00:02:23,226
- Stop resisting!
- [Jovi] Get over here!

48
00:02:23,893 --> 00:02:25,019
[inhales sharply] Where's Doc Reyes?

49
00:02:25,103 --> 00:02:26,104
Sir, they were dragged in there!

50
00:02:26,980 --> 00:02:28,439
With Nurse Jamilah!

51
00:02:28,523 --> 00:02:31,109
[suspenseful sting]

52
00:02:34,195 --> 00:02:36,072
[clamoring]

53
00:02:37,323 --> 00:02:37,949
[officer] Take care of them.

54
00:02:38,032 --> 00:02:39,701
- [policeman 1] Quick! Move!
- [policeman 2] Get in!

55
00:02:41,035 --> 00:02:41,995
Sir, we'll leave them in your care.

56
00:02:43,663 --> 00:02:45,874
- Thank you so much, sir.
- It's nothing.

57
00:02:45,957 --> 00:02:47,000
[policeman] You're all safe now!

58
00:02:49,544 --> 00:02:51,713
[sobbing] Miss, do you know Jamilah?

59
00:02:51,796 --> 00:02:53,214
She's also a nurse here.

60
00:02:53,298 --> 00:02:55,341
- She's still inside.
- [Norhana] Thank you.

61
00:02:56,759 --> 00:02:57,969
- [Jovi] Get over here!
- Huh?!

62
00:02:58,052 --> 00:02:59,637
- Where are you taking Doc?!
- [Teresa] Jamilah!

63
00:02:59,721 --> 00:03:01,347
- [Jovi] Come!
- Jamilah!

64
00:03:01,431 --> 00:03:02,765
Leave Tommy to me. Go on ahead.

65
00:03:02,849 --> 00:03:03,683
‪[heavy breathing]

66
00:03:04,601 --> 00:03:06,185
- You sure?
- It's better if we split up.

67
00:03:06,269 --> 00:03:07,478
- Stay still!
- Let's meet up upstairs.

68
00:03:07,562 --> 00:03:08,855
[Jamilah] What're you going to do to Doc?!

69
00:03:08,938 --> 00:03:10,273
- [Jovi] Let's go! Let's go!
- [Axl] Move!

70
00:03:10,356 --> 00:03:11,482
[Jamilah] Doc!

71
00:03:11,566 --> 00:03:14,068
[tense music continues]

72
00:03:14,152 --> 00:03:15,820
We need to split up.

73
00:03:21,159 --> 00:03:22,285
I'll go this way.

74
00:03:27,707 --> 00:03:30,001
- Let me go!
- Just do as I say!

75
00:03:36,883 --> 00:03:38,218
[officer] Come on! Quick!

76
00:03:38,801 --> 00:03:40,094
[indistinct]

77
00:03:40,178 --> 00:03:41,012
[officer] Take it easy.

78
00:03:43,181 --> 00:03:44,432
[Felix, in English] Good job!

79
00:03:44,515 --> 00:03:45,975
[in English] Stay sharp.

80
00:03:46,059 --> 00:03:47,769
[in English] Secure the perimeter.

81
00:03:47,852 --> 00:03:49,145
Adani, let's head back.

82
00:03:49,229 --> 00:03:50,855
[Norhana sobbing] Jamilah is still nowhere

83
00:03:50,939 --> 00:03:53,608
to be found, Omar! Just what
happened to that child?

84
00:03:53,691 --> 00:03:55,568
[clicks tongue] Move quickly!

85
00:03:56,945 --> 00:03:58,404
Even Doc Reyes…

86
00:03:58,488 --> 00:04:00,073
- She's not part of those who are rescued.
- [Norhana sobs]

87
00:04:01,324 --> 00:04:03,326
Why won't you let us go?

88
00:04:03,409 --> 00:04:05,703
Dr. Teresa and I already
treated your brother.

89
00:04:05,787 --> 00:04:06,871
What more do you want?!

90
00:04:06,955 --> 00:04:08,248
- Just shut your mouth!
- [Jamilah shrieking]

91
00:04:08,331 --> 00:04:10,667
Just do as I say. Understand?

92
00:04:11,251 --> 00:04:13,294
- [Jamilah panting] Okay.
- Jovi.

93
00:04:13,962 --> 00:04:15,171
- Just leave me behind.
- [somber music playing]

94
00:04:15,672 --> 00:04:16,881
What did you say?

95
00:04:18,508 --> 00:04:20,301
Jovi, just leave me behind.

96
00:04:21,344 --> 00:04:22,845
Save yourself.

97
00:04:23,805 --> 00:04:25,640
I'm just going to be a burden to you.

98
00:04:26,140 --> 00:04:29,852
[somber music playing]

99
00:04:31,562 --> 00:04:32,397
‪[sniffs]

100
00:04:34,232 --> 00:04:36,442
[sniffles]

101
00:04:38,361 --> 00:04:39,404
Head inside for now.

102
00:04:48,413 --> 00:04:49,372
‪[Jovi mutters]

103
00:04:49,872 --> 00:04:50,957
Don't move.

104
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:53,084
- [Axl hisses, grunts]
- [grunting]

105
00:04:53,668 --> 00:04:55,670
[Teresa grunts, sobbing]

106
00:04:55,753 --> 00:04:57,714
[Teresa sobs] Surrender already!

107
00:04:57,797 --> 00:05:01,884
Think about your brother!
His condition might get worse!

108
00:05:01,968 --> 00:05:03,344
If you don't shut up…

109
00:05:03,428 --> 00:05:04,304
[Teresa sobs]

110
00:05:04,387 --> 00:05:05,430
…I'll make you.

111
00:05:05,513 --> 00:05:06,556
[Axl] Stand up.

112
00:05:07,598 --> 00:05:08,641
Stand up!

113
00:05:09,517 --> 00:05:11,936
[sobbing]

114
00:05:12,520 --> 00:05:14,397
Just go, Jovi!

115
00:05:15,273 --> 00:05:16,316
Go on!

116
00:05:16,399 --> 00:05:20,945
[tense music playing]

117
00:05:27,076 --> 00:05:29,078
[music softens]

118
00:05:32,623 --> 00:05:34,584
Defend yourself, okay?

119
00:05:34,667 --> 00:05:35,501
[Tommy sniffles]

120
00:05:35,585 --> 00:05:36,711
You're strong.

121
00:05:36,794 --> 00:05:38,588
[mutters]

122
00:05:38,671 --> 00:05:39,630
[softly] I trust you.

123
00:05:40,923 --> 00:05:41,758
[sniffles]

124
00:05:41,841 --> 00:05:43,217
Be careful, Jovi.

125
00:05:43,718 --> 00:05:45,386
I'll come back for you. [sniffs]

126
00:05:46,220 --> 00:05:47,305
Stay here.

127
00:05:49,640 --> 00:05:51,100
‪[Jovi sniffs, sighs]

128
00:05:51,893 --> 00:05:53,227
Move.

129
00:05:53,311 --> 00:05:55,021
- I said, move! Go!
- [tense music playing]

130
00:05:55,813 --> 00:05:57,148
Go.

131
00:05:58,316 --> 00:06:00,151
This way. Go.

132
00:06:05,740 --> 00:06:06,657
‪[tense dramatic music playing]

133
00:06:08,534 --> 00:06:09,911
[thug yells]

134
00:06:11,579 --> 00:06:12,955
[grunting]

135
00:06:15,291 --> 00:06:16,834
[thug 2 yells]

136
00:06:26,094 --> 00:06:28,387
[suspenseful music playing]

137
00:06:35,061 --> 00:06:35,895
‪[gunshots blasting]

138
00:06:45,613 --> 00:06:47,490
[grunting]

139
00:06:53,287 --> 00:06:55,039
[suspenseful music continues]

140
00:07:08,886 --> 00:07:09,804
Jamilah?

141
00:07:09,887 --> 00:07:11,305
[Jalil] Jamilah!

142
00:07:13,307 --> 00:07:14,142
‪[gasps]

143
00:07:17,687 --> 00:07:18,896
[grunts]

144
00:07:20,773 --> 00:07:22,150
[grunting and groaning]

145
00:07:23,484 --> 00:07:24,318
[grunts]

146
00:07:28,865 --> 00:07:29,824
[grunts]

147
00:07:31,075 --> 00:07:32,243
[groans]

148
00:07:34,495 --> 00:07:35,621
My turn!

149
00:07:35,705 --> 00:07:38,666
[both grunting]

150
00:07:46,591 --> 00:07:47,425
‪[grunts]

151
00:07:47,508 --> 00:07:48,342
‪[grunting]

152
00:07:56,225 --> 00:07:57,894
[grunts loudly]

153
00:07:57,977 --> 00:07:58,811
‪[grunting]

154
00:08:27,965 --> 00:08:30,384
[breathing heavily]

155
00:08:30,468 --> 00:08:35,264
[suspenseful music playing]

156
00:08:47,360 --> 00:08:49,070
Jamilah! [heavy breathing]

157
00:08:49,153 --> 00:08:50,655
Jamilah… [heavy breathing]

158
00:08:56,661 --> 00:08:57,495
‪[system beeping]

159
00:09:05,628 --> 00:09:06,921
[Teresa] Help!

160
00:09:07,505 --> 00:09:09,799
- Let me go!
- Shut up!

161
00:09:09,882 --> 00:09:10,716
‪[system beeping]

162
00:09:12,343 --> 00:09:13,427
Agent Reyes?

163
00:09:13,511 --> 00:09:15,471
[Lara] <i>Agent Reyes. Marcus! Marcus!</i>

164
00:09:15,555 --> 00:09:17,348
<i>I've located Miss Teresa.</i>

165
00:09:21,269 --> 00:09:22,228
Where is she, Lara?

166
00:09:22,937 --> 00:09:23,980
‪[system beeping]

167
00:09:25,439 --> 00:09:26,983
[Teresa sobs] Help!

168
00:09:27,066 --> 00:09:28,484
- Just let me go!
- Shut up!

169
00:09:28,568 --> 00:09:29,777
I said, shut up!

170
00:09:29,860 --> 00:09:31,612
[Teresa sobbing]

171
00:09:31,696 --> 00:09:33,823
[system beeping]

172
00:09:33,906 --> 00:09:35,449
Wait… Um…

173
00:09:36,033 --> 00:09:38,077
They have another hostage.

174
00:09:38,869 --> 00:09:39,912
Uh…

175
00:09:40,663 --> 00:09:41,914
Uh…

176
00:09:42,999 --> 00:09:44,542
A Muslim girl?

177
00:09:44,625 --> 00:09:48,004
[music intensifies]

178
00:09:48,087 --> 00:09:49,255
Jamilah.

179
00:09:51,007 --> 00:09:51,924
[Teresa sobs]

180
00:09:52,008 --> 00:09:53,342
Shh!

181
00:09:53,426 --> 00:09:54,510
Keep quiet.

182
00:09:54,594 --> 00:09:55,970
[sobbing]

183
00:09:57,138 --> 00:09:58,097
Lara, where is she?

184
00:09:58,180 --> 00:09:59,015
‪[system beeping]

185
00:10:02,393 --> 00:10:04,520
Agent Reyes, they’re headed
for the north wing.

186
00:10:05,688 --> 00:10:07,690
[Lara, in English] <i>Exit the stairwell,</i>
<i>and then break right.</i>

187
00:10:07,773 --> 00:10:09,317
- That’ll lead you to the north wing.
- [radio static]

188
00:10:09,400 --> 00:10:11,235
[suspenseful music playing]

189
00:10:11,319 --> 00:10:12,153
‪[system beeping]

190
00:10:22,830 --> 00:10:24,373
Shh!

191
00:10:24,457 --> 00:10:26,250
- [Teresa whimpers softly]
- Shh!

192
00:10:29,253 --> 00:10:31,130
[sucks teeth, grunts angrily]

193
00:10:33,549 --> 00:10:36,177
- Where are you taking me?! [sobbing]
- [softly] Keep walking.

194
00:10:37,094 --> 00:10:37,928
Keep walking!

195
00:10:38,012 --> 00:10:40,139
[suspenseful music continues]

196
00:10:41,057 --> 00:10:41,974
‪[gasps, whimpers]

197
00:10:44,935 --> 00:10:47,104
[gasps]

198
00:10:47,188 --> 00:10:49,357
[sobs] Let me go!

199
00:10:54,612 --> 00:10:55,821
[Jamilah yelps]

200
00:10:56,322 --> 00:10:57,281
Help!

201
00:11:02,495 --> 00:11:04,246
[in English] I have eyes on one suspect.

202
00:11:04,330 --> 00:11:06,957
He’s got Jamilah, a nurse.

203
00:11:08,959 --> 00:11:12,463
Reyes, save that hostage.

204
00:11:13,089 --> 00:11:15,091
- [Teresa] Let me go!
- Stop resisting!

205
00:11:15,925 --> 00:11:17,343
[Jalil] Stop!

206
00:11:17,426 --> 00:11:18,511
Freeze!

207
00:11:18,594 --> 00:11:20,554
[tense music playing]

208
00:11:23,599 --> 00:11:26,227
Reyes, I’ll save your mother.

209
00:11:37,780 --> 00:11:41,117
[tense music playing]

210
00:11:42,868 --> 00:11:44,829
[Jamilah] Let me go!

211
00:11:45,913 --> 00:11:47,248
Let me go!

212
00:11:47,957 --> 00:11:48,999
[Jovi] Drop it!

213
00:11:50,292 --> 00:11:51,502
Drop your weapon!

214
00:11:51,585 --> 00:11:52,420
[Jamilah sobs]

215
00:11:52,503 --> 00:11:53,587
[Jovi] Drop it!

216
00:11:56,048 --> 00:11:58,717
- Don't hurt her.
- I'll kill her!

217
00:12:03,013 --> 00:12:04,598
[music intensifies]

218
00:12:07,560 --> 00:12:09,103
Release her.

219
00:12:10,563 --> 00:12:11,856
Fight me instead.

220
00:12:13,023 --> 00:12:14,191
Put it down!

221
00:12:16,902 --> 00:12:17,695
Put it down!

222
00:12:18,904 --> 00:12:20,781
[exhales]

223
00:12:20,865 --> 00:12:22,908
- [Jamilah] Please.
- [gun clatters]

224
00:12:25,035 --> 00:12:26,370
I'm unarmed.

225
00:12:30,249 --> 00:12:31,375
Look.

226
00:12:35,045 --> 00:12:36,046
I'm putting it down.

227
00:12:41,302 --> 00:12:42,136
‪[Jamilah gasps]

228
00:12:47,641 --> 00:12:49,768
[Jamilah exclaims, grunts]

229
00:12:49,852 --> 00:12:52,021
- [tense music continues]
- [Jamilah panting]

230
00:12:52,771 --> 00:12:53,606
‪[music intensifies]

231
00:13:03,616 --> 00:13:05,159
[in Arabic] In the name of Allah.

232
00:13:05,951 --> 00:13:08,829
- [Jalil grunts]
- [Axl grunts, groans]

233
00:13:08,913 --> 00:13:11,499
[both grunting]

234
00:13:18,380 --> 00:13:21,634
- [Jalil grunts]
- [Axl groans, panting]

235
00:13:24,303 --> 00:13:27,389
- [tense music playing]
- [groans]

236
00:13:29,850 --> 00:13:30,809
Coward!

237
00:13:30,893 --> 00:13:31,727
‪[music intensifies]

238
00:13:39,235 --> 00:13:40,444
[Axl grunts]

239
00:13:41,654 --> 00:13:43,322
[shouts violently]

240
00:13:43,405 --> 00:13:44,865
[both grunting]

241
00:13:52,248 --> 00:13:53,707
[both grunting]

242
00:13:54,375 --> 00:13:55,209
‪[both grunt]

243
00:14:01,340 --> 00:14:02,174
‪[Jovi grunts]

244
00:14:08,389 --> 00:14:10,182
[Axl grunting]

245
00:14:11,141 --> 00:14:12,351
- [grunting]
- [bone cracks]

246
00:14:13,978 --> 00:14:15,938
[music intensifies]

247
00:14:20,526 --> 00:14:24,154
- [Axl grunting, shouting]
- [Jalil groaning]

248
00:14:28,951 --> 00:14:30,911
‪[tense dramatic music thudding]

249
00:14:40,004 --> 00:14:41,297
‪[tense dramatic music playing]

250
00:14:43,048 --> 00:14:44,049
[Jamilah exclaims]

251
00:14:44,133 --> 00:14:45,551
[shouts in pain]

252
00:14:45,634 --> 00:14:47,303
[Jovi grunts]

253
00:14:51,390 --> 00:14:53,392
[music intensifies]

254
00:14:59,607 --> 00:15:01,525
- [gasps]
- Doc?

255
00:15:01,609 --> 00:15:05,696
- [both breathing heavily]
- [music subdues]

256
00:15:06,989 --> 00:15:08,157
Doc, get up.

257
00:15:12,286 --> 00:15:13,495
Are you okay?

258
00:15:14,830 --> 00:15:16,123
Are you hurt, Doc?

259
00:15:16,665 --> 00:15:19,209
[somber music playing]

260
00:15:19,293 --> 00:15:20,127
‪[heavy breathing]

261
00:15:27,134 --> 00:15:28,218
[in English] Base.

262
00:15:28,761 --> 00:15:30,304
[sighs sharply]

263
00:15:31,347 --> 00:15:33,682
[in English] Hostage clear.
Target secured.

264
00:15:33,766 --> 00:15:34,600
‪[heavy breathing]

265
00:15:36,727 --> 00:15:38,228
Espina, what's your status?

266
00:15:39,939 --> 00:15:41,398
[in English] Hostage secured.

267
00:15:42,316 --> 00:15:43,734
Your mother is safe.

268
00:15:52,326 --> 00:15:53,452
Thank you.

269
00:15:57,623 --> 00:16:00,376
[melancholic music playing]

270
00:16:08,801 --> 00:16:09,635
‪[dramatic sting]

271
00:16:19,770 --> 00:16:20,854
Are you okay?

272
00:16:24,274 --> 00:16:26,318
[ominous sting]

273
00:16:36,453 --> 00:16:37,663
I'm okay.

274
00:16:39,248 --> 00:16:40,541
Are you sure?

275
00:16:42,876 --> 00:16:44,128
You don't have any injuries?

276
00:16:45,629 --> 00:16:49,091
‪[dramatic flourishes]

277
00:16:50,843 --> 00:16:52,177
[gasps, inhales]

278
00:16:54,096 --> 00:16:55,055
[in English] Sorry.

279
00:16:57,558 --> 00:17:00,185
I'm just making sure that you're safe.

280
00:17:07,526 --> 00:17:08,944
Thank you.

281
00:17:09,695 --> 00:17:11,280
Thank you, too, Jamilah.

282
00:17:13,073 --> 00:17:16,368
[melancholic music continues]

283
00:17:19,371 --> 00:17:24,084
[breathing shakily]

284
00:17:27,755 --> 00:17:32,926
- Hurry up!
- [grunting]

285
00:17:33,010 --> 00:17:35,095
[gasping, shouting]

286
00:17:38,640 --> 00:17:41,977
Let me go! [screams]

287
00:17:42,061 --> 00:17:43,145
[Axl groaning]

288
00:17:50,778 --> 00:17:51,695
Ma!

289
00:17:53,447 --> 00:17:55,866
[crying]

290
00:18:06,835 --> 00:18:08,378
[sighs]

291
00:18:15,761 --> 00:18:17,763
I thought I'd lose you, too.

292
00:18:17,846 --> 00:18:20,557
[emotional music playing]

293
00:18:32,069 --> 00:18:36,073
[tense music playing]

294
00:18:51,338 --> 00:18:54,091
- [Omar] <i>What are you planning?</i>
- I can't tell you yet.

295
00:18:54,174 --> 00:18:56,218
[Jalil] <i>So don't look for me, Uncle.</i>

296
00:18:56,301 --> 00:18:58,011
<i>It's for your safety.</i>

297
00:19:03,976 --> 00:19:07,271
[melancholic music playing]

298
00:19:21,618 --> 00:19:22,911
[Felix] Sir Marcus.

299
00:19:26,415 --> 00:19:29,751
- [policeman 1] Congratulations, sir.
- [policeman 2] Congratulations, sir.

300
00:19:29,835 --> 00:19:33,714
[in English] Congratulations.
Mission accomplished. Finally.

301
00:19:34,882 --> 00:19:36,341
- [policeman 3] Congratulations, sir.
- Congratulations.

302
00:19:36,425 --> 00:19:38,677
- [policeman 4] Good job.
- We had faith in you, sir.

303
00:19:38,760 --> 00:19:39,761
[man] Congratulations.

304
00:19:39,845 --> 00:19:41,471
[Felix] So, will we celebrate?

305
00:19:41,555 --> 00:19:43,182
[chuckles softly]

306
00:19:43,265 --> 00:19:44,391
[clears throat]

307
00:19:49,813 --> 00:19:51,398
[indistinct speech]

308
00:19:52,191 --> 00:19:53,275
- [Felix] So…
- Let's go.

309
00:20:07,664 --> 00:20:08,832
Thank you.

310
00:20:11,084 --> 00:20:12,669
You saved my mother.

311
00:20:14,046 --> 00:20:15,297
Thank you, too.

312
00:20:16,465 --> 00:20:17,758
For what?

313
00:20:17,841 --> 00:20:19,468
For saving my--

314
00:20:20,219 --> 00:20:22,095
[suspenseful music playing]

315
00:20:25,432 --> 00:20:27,184
For saving our fellow Muslim.

316
00:20:28,560 --> 00:20:29,811
Thank you, Reyes.

317
00:20:33,440 --> 00:20:35,692
[dramatic music playing]

318
00:21:05,597 --> 00:21:09,643
This hostage-taking
at S. Trinidad Hospital is insane.

319
00:21:09,726 --> 00:21:10,644
Amazing!

320
00:21:10,727 --> 00:21:14,022
Task Force Alpha's rescue was shown now!

321
00:21:14,106 --> 00:21:15,774
Our country is still in danger!

322
00:21:15,857 --> 00:21:18,151
[Azuelo] <i>Team Task Force Alpha.</i>

323
00:21:18,235 --> 00:21:19,403
- [shouts]
- [cheering]

324
00:21:19,486 --> 00:21:20,737
[cheering]

325
00:21:20,821 --> 00:21:22,072
- [Norhana] Jamilah!
- [Jamilah] Aunty!

326
00:21:22,155 --> 00:21:24,199
What's important is that I'm safe!

327
00:21:24,283 --> 00:21:26,576
[Omar] <i>How will I explain this</i>
<i>to your side?</i>

328
00:21:26,660 --> 00:21:28,370
[Marcus] Our mission was a success

329
00:21:28,453 --> 00:21:30,205
thanks to the coordinated efforts
of the entire team.

330
00:21:30,289 --> 00:21:32,958
[Azuelo] <i>They will personally lead us</i>

331
00:21:33,041 --> 00:21:37,629
<i>to the syndicates supplying</i>
<i>high-powered firearms.</i>

332
00:21:38,547 --> 00:21:40,090
- [people screaming]
- [gunshots]

333
00:21:40,173 --> 00:21:41,341
[Marcus] <i>Look for evidence.</i>

334
00:21:41,425 --> 00:21:42,968
[tense music playing]

335
00:21:45,929 --> 00:21:48,432
- This establishment…
- [in English] Listen up, all units.

336
00:21:48,515 --> 00:21:49,599
<i>Target the priority.</i>

337
00:21:49,683 --> 00:21:51,476
[Ahmd] <i>Someone is pulling their strings.</i>

338
00:21:51,560 --> 00:21:53,228
<i>Someone is doing this on purpose.</i>
